	<h1 class="title">今年的诺贝尔文学奖，写的是切尔诺贝利和苏军女战士的真实故事</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/120946/small/120946.jpg?1437229437" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">Alexandra Alter</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-10-09 13:48:27 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/15828/medium/15828.jpeg?1444368621" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


